      <title>Sirius XM 因“令人沮丧”的取消流程被纽约州起诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-20/sirius-xm-is-sued-by-ny-over-frustrating-cancellation-process</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Sirius XM Radio Inc. 被纽约州起诉，称其让客户难以取消订阅该广播公司的在线广播服务，违反了州和联邦消费者保护法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-20/sirius-xm-is-sued-by-ny-over-frustrating-cancellation-process</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Dec 2023 15:38:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲最大的本土电池制造商获得 12 亿美元资金以提高产量</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-20/northvolt-raises-another-1-2-billion-to-fund-battery-ramp-up</link>
      <description><![CDATA[电池制造商 Northvolt AB 已从国际投资者那里筹集了 12 亿美元，该公司旨在提高其位于瑞典北部的工厂的产量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-20/northvolt-raises-another-1-2-billion-to-fund-battery-ramp-up</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Dec 2023 15:03:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国将华为从核心网络中撤出的最后期限临近，英国电信面临罚款风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-20/bt-risks-fine-as-uk-deadline-looms-for-pulling-huawei-from-core</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国电信集团表示，在英国政府 12 月 31 日的最后期限之前，其核心网络中尚未完成更换华为技术有限公司设备的工作。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-20/bt-risks-fine-as-uk-deadline-looms-for-pulling-huawei-from-core</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Dec 2023 12:39:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国最高法院裁定人工智能机器人缺乏人情味而无法成为发明家</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-20/ai-can-t-be-named-as-inventor-for-patents-uk-s-top-court-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国最高法院在一项重要裁决中表示，人工智能程序不能被列为专利发明人，拒绝将机器置于与人类近乎平等的地位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-20/ai-can-t-be-named-as-inventor-for-patents-uk-s-top-court-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Dec 2023 09:57:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
